00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:11.520
Good as new, only better.

00:03:11.520 --> 00:03:13.520
And what about these jeans?

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:16.520
You've seen them once, you've seen them a thousand times,

00:03:16.520 --> 00:03:18.520
but by just roughing them up.

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:21.520
Now new jeans look like old jeans,

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:23.520
which makes them even newer jeans.

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:24.520
It's a whole new concept.

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:27.520
I guess it's just a matter of looking at an old thing in a new light.

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:30.520
