00:05:17.870 --> 00:05:19.870
How can that improve our lives?

00:05:19.870 --> 00:05:21.870
Well, if it's something old and really annoying,

00:05:21.870 --> 00:05:24.870
we can make it new by getting rid of the annoying part.

00:05:24.870 --> 00:05:25.870
Hey, I know.

00:05:25.870 --> 00:05:29.870
