My mom always calls me from the road on Mother's Day.

00:11:08.900 --> 00:11:10.900
Well, it's not this Sunday.

00:11:10.900 --> 00:11:14.900
It's not next Sunday or the Sunday after that or that or that.

00:11:14.900 --> 00:11:16.900
When is Mother's Day anyway?

00:11:16.900 --> 00:11:18.900
Why are you so anxious for it to be Mother's Day?

00:11:18.900 --> 00:11:21.900
