00:11:26.530 --> 00:11:28.530
To the best mom in the world.

00:11:28.530 --> 00:11:31.530
Why would your mom be making a Mother's Day card?

00:11:31.530 --> 00:11:32.530
Good question.

00:11:32.530 --> 00:11:34.530
