And the big old mommy bird has a big old empty nest.

00:12:23.530 --> 00:12:25.530
No one to feed worms to.

00:12:25.530 --> 00:12:28.530
So you think my mom's afraid that we're all going to be leaving the nest soon?

00:12:28.530 --> 00:12:29.530
That's right.

00:12:29.530 --> 00:12:31.530
She's feeling unwanted, unneeded.

00:12:31.530 --> 00:12:33.530
